<section class="py-5 bg-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title text-center mb-5">The Art of Fine Tailoring</h2>

    <!-- Row 1: The Perfect Fit -->
    <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
      <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
        <img src="~/images/img/feat1.jpg" alt="Cuahang" class="img-fluid rounded shadow">
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <h3 class="mb-3">Đa đang kiểu loại. Tìm mỏi con mắt luôn.</h3>
        <p>Đầy đủ các kiểu dáng. Phù hợp cho mọi lứa tuổi. At Elegant Suits, we believe that a well-fitted suit is the
          cornerstone of a gentleman's wardrobe. Our master tailors take precise measurements to ensure that every suit
          complements your unique physique.</p>
        <p>A properly tailored suit doesn't just enhance your appearance—it boosts your confidence and commands respect
          in every room you enter.</p>
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mt-4">
          <div class="me-4">
            <i class="fas fa-ruler-combined fa-2x text-secondary"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h5 class="mb-1">Expert Measurements</h5>
            <p class="mb-0">Over 20 precise measurements taken for each client</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Row 2: Premium Materials -->
    <div class="row align-items-center mb-5 flex-lg-row-reverse">
      <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
        <img src="~/images/img/maydo.jpg" alt="Maydo" class="img-fluid rounded shadow">
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <h3 class="mb-3">không tìm thấy mẫu ứng ý?</h3>
        <p>Với hơn 500 mẫu có sẵn, chúng tôi sẽ "tùy chỉnh" lại một bộ suit dành riêng cho bạn. Tha hồ lựa chọn kiểu
          dáng, kích thước không giới hạn, chất liệu vải đa dạng. We source only the finest fabrics from renowned mills
          in Italy, England, and Scotland. From luxurious Super 150s wool to breathable linen and sophisticated cashmere
          blends, our selection caters to every climate and occasion.</p>
        <p>The quality of our materials ensures comfort, durability, and an impeccable drape that distinguishes our
          suits from mass-produced alternatives.</p>
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mt-4">
          <div class="me-4">
            <i class="fas fa-certificate fa-2x text-secondary"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h5 class="mb-1">Superior Quality</h5>
            <p class="mb-0">Ethically sourced premium materials with certification</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Row 3: Craftsmanship -->
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
        <img src="~/images/img/wall2.jpg" alt="chomuon" class="img-fluid rounded shadow">
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <h3 class="mb-3">Tiết kiệm chi phí. Không lo về giá!</h3>
        <p>Bạn chỉ đi dự tiệc có một lần nhưng phải mua hẳn một bộ suit ? Đừng lo, bên chúng tôi sẽ cho bạn mượn. Our
          suits blend traditional tailoring techniques with contemporary designs to create timeless pieces that never go
          out of style. Each suit requires over 60 hours of meticulous handwork by our skilled artisans.</p>
        <p>From hand-stitched lapels to precisely aligned patterns, every detail is crafted to perfection, resulting in
          suits that tell a story of excellence and attention to detail.</p>
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mt-4">
          <div class="me-4">
            <i class="fas fa-hands fa-2x text-secondary"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h5 class="mb-1">Artisan Crafted</h5>
            <p class="mb-0">Each suit passes through 20 skilled craftspeople</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Visit Store CTA -->
    <div class="text-center mt-5">
      <a href="about.html" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">Learn More About Our Process</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


